websphinx
Class LinkEvent

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--websphinx.LinkEvent
public class LinkEvent
extends java.lang.Object

Link event. A LinkEvent is issued when the crawler starts or stops retrieving a link, and when it makes a decision about a link.
